  EffectDiscription_ENG: 'When you trash this card in your hand using one of your
    effects, if [Eyesmon: Scatter Mode] is in your trash, you may play this card
    without paying its memory cost. [Your Turn] For each [Eyesmon: Scatter Mode]
    in your trash, this Digimon gets +2000 DP.'
